SEMINAR - Topic 7 (Phân tích dữ liệu thông minh - CQ2018/21)¶

Giảng viên: Nguyễn Tiến Huy¶

Thng tin nhm:

STT: 12

Thnh vin:

  • ng Hu Thng - MSSV: 18120555 (Nhm trng)
  • Nguyn Trung Thnh - MSSV: 18120565
  • Phm Xun Thnh - MSSV: 18120567
  • ng Minh Th - MSSV: 18120579

Giới thiệu chung¶

y l cuc thi trn Kaggle v d on gi nh, vi d liu l thng tin cc ngi nh thnh ph Ames, bang Iowa, M. D liu ny c cung cp bi Dean De Cock cho mc ch ging dy v hc tp.

Link cuc thi: House Prices - Advanced Regression Techniques

Hnh thc nh gi: Dng li Root-Mean-Squared-Error (RMSE) vi log(gi tr d on) v log(gi tr thc t)

Các đặc trưng khác¶

Sau khi c data_description.txt, c 2 iu m mnh quan tm:

  • Nhng c trng no s c kh nng nh hng ln n SalePrice
  • C kh nhiu c trng (khng bao gm SalePrice) c s tng quan vi nhau. VD: GarageArea v GarageCars

Nhng c trng s c kh nng nh hng ln n SalePrice:

  • Neighborhood: khu vc trong thnh ph Ames m ngi nh thuc (thuc khu ph no, v d nh: Old Town, Timberland, ...)
  • OverallQual: cht lng tng th v hon thin ca cn nh
  • YearRemodAdd: nm tu sa, xy thm
  • GrLivArea: din tch s dng
  • GarageArea: din tch garage

Tuy nhin, kim tra, chng ta s dng Corr()

# Tin hnh label encode cho cc ct catogorical khng  dng s thnh s  c th tnh c corr nhm ko b st c trng no quan trng

In [27]:
full_df['PoolQC'] = full_df['PoolQC'].fillna('no_pool')
full_df['MiscFeature'] = full_df['MiscFeature'].fillna('none')
full_df['Alley'] = full_df['Alley'].fillna('no_alley_access')
full_df['Fence'] = full_df['Fence'].fillna('no_fence')
full_df['FireplaceQu'] = full_df['FireplaceQu'].fillna('no_fireplace')

for col in ['GarageFinish', 'GarageQual', 'GarageCond', 'GarageType']:
    full_df[col] = full_df[col].fillna('no_garage')
for col in ['BsmtQual', 'BsmtCond', 'BsmtExposure', 'BsmtFinType1', 'BsmtFinType2']:
    full_df[col] = full_df[col].fillna('no_basement')
    
full_df["Functional"] = full_df["Functional"].fillna("typical")
In [28]:
full_df["LotFrontage"] = full_df.groupby("Neighborhood")["LotFrontage"].transform(lambda x: x.fillna(x.mean()))
In [29]:

Model và Predict¶

RIDGE REGRESSION¶

Linear Regression: ||y - Xw||^2_2 (RSS)¶

Ridge Regression: ||y - Xw||^2_2 + alpha * ||w||^2_2¶

  • Hi quy Ridge (Ridge Regression) l mt thut ton nng cp ca thut ton hi quy tuyn tnh (Linear Regression).

  • S khc bit (nng cp) ca Ridge so vi Linear ch:

    • Ridge c th khc phc hin tng Ovefitting xy ra Linear

    • Trong khi Linear tm cch ti thiu ha (minimize) tng bnh phng phn d (RSS), cn Ridge c thm alpha * ||w||^2_2 vi alpha (alpha > 0) gi l tham s hiu chnh (tuning parameter) ca m hnh

    • Tham s alpha th hin s u tin gia cc i lng ca tp d liu

      • alpha ln: dn n undefitting
      • alpha nh: Tr v thnh Linear (dn n overfitting)
    • Vic la chn tham s alpha rt quan trng, y ta dng phng php cross-validation chn
    • Cross-validation c tch hp sn trong RidgeCV
In [39]:
from sklearn.linear_model import RidgeCV
from sklearn.model_selection import KFold
from sklearn.linear_model import Ridge

from sklearn.linear_model import LassoCV
from sklearn.linear_model import Lasso
from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression

K-Fold CV s gip chng ta nh gi mt model y v chnh xc hn khi chng ta c mt tp d liu khng ln.

  • Phn d liu Training th s c chia ngu nhin thnh K phn (K l mt s nguyn, hay chn l 5 hoc 10).
  • Sau train model K ln, mi ln train s chn 1 phn lm d liu validation v K-1 phn cn li lm d liu training.
  • Kt qu nh gi model cui cng s l trung bnh cng kt qu nh gi ca K ln train.

Alpha: y chng ta s kho st b gi tr ca alpha = (1e-8, 1e-4, 1e-2, 1.0, 10.0, 20.0, 50.0, 100.0) chn ra alpha tt nht cho m hnh

In [40]:
# Phng thc kFold
splitter = KFold(5, random_state=42, shuffle=True)

# Cc gi tr alpha i din cn kim tra
alps = [1e-8, 1e-4, 1e-2, 1.0, 10.0, 20.0, 50.0, 100.0]
scores =  np.array([])
for alp in alps:
    tmpRidge = RidgeCV(alphas=(alp, alp), cv=splitter)
    tmpRidge.fit(train, y_train)
    scores= np.append(scores, [tmpRidge.best_score_])

scores = scores.transpose()

fig, ax = plt.subplots(1, 1, figsize=(17,7))
ax.plot(alps, scores, ls='-', marker='o')
ax.set_xscale('log')
ax.set_xlabel('$alpha$')
ax.set_ylabel('best scores');

T th, ta c th thy hm t best score cao nht xp x 0.92 ti alpha bng 10.0.

Dự đoán: alpha = 10.0 là giá trị cần tìm¶

Tiếp theo ta tiến hành tìm tham số alpha tốt nhất¶

  • So khp trn tp train bng phng php Cross-validation tm ra tham s alpha tt nht
In [41]:
ridgeCV_object = RidgeCV(alphas=(1e-8, 1e-4, 1e-2, 1.0, 10.0, 20.0, 50.0, 100.0), cv=splitter)
ridgeCV_object.fit(train, y_train)

print("Best model searched:\nbest score = {}\nalpha = {}\nintercept = {}, ".format(ridgeCV_object.best_score_,
                                                                                                ridgeCV_object.alpha_,
                                                                                                 ridgeCV_object.intercept_,
                                                                                                 ))      
best_alpha = ridgeCV_object.alpha_

Lasso regression¶

  • Ging vi Ridge Regression, Lasso Regression l mt loi phn tch hi quy s dng k thut chun ha L1.

  • Phng php ny s dng mt hnh pht nh hng n gi tr ca cc h s hi quy. Khi hnh pht tng nhiu h s tr thnh s khng v ngc li.

  • Lasso Regression: (1 / (2 * n_samples)) * ||y - Xw||^2_2 + alpha * ||w||_1

  • V mt k thut, m hnh Lasso ang ti u ha chc nng mc tiu ging nh Elastic Net vi l1_ratio=1.0(khng c hnh pht L2).

In [44]:
splitter = KFold(5, random_state=42, shuffle=True)

alps = [1e-8, 1e-4, 1e-2, 1.0, 10.0, 20.0, 50.0, 100.0]
scores =  np.array([])
for alp in alps:
    tmpLasso = LassoCV(alphas=(alp, alp), cv=splitter)
    tmpLasso.fit(train, y_train)
    scores= np.append(scores, [tmpLasso.dual_gap_])

scores = scores.transpose()

fig, ax = plt.subplots(1, 1, figsize=(17,7))
ax.plot(alps, scores, ls='-', marker='o')
ax.set_xscale('log')
ax.set_xlabel('$alpha$')
ax.set_ylabel('dual_gap_');

Tìm tham số alpha tốt nhất¶

In [45]:
lassoCV_object = LassoCV(alphas=(1e-8, 1e-4, 1e-2, 1.0, 10.0, 20.0, 50.0, 100.0), cv=splitter)
lassoCV_object.fit(train, y_train)

print("Best model searched:\ndual_gap_ = {}\nalpha = {}\nintercept = {}, ".format(lassoCV_object.dual_gap_,
                                                                                                lassoCV_object.alpha_,
                                                                                                 lassoCV_object.intercept_
                                                                                                 ))
